  "blurb": "A contemporary two-bedroom deluxe residence of around 173 m² in the gated Laguna resort enclave at Bang Tao, Phuket, with lagoon and ocean views, a full kitchen and a private balcony. Minutes from Bang Tao Beach, Boat Avenue and the golf course.",
  "detail": "Part of a contemporary residence in the Laguna resort lands at Bang Tao, this two-bedroom deluxe home spans around 173 square metres on a single level, framing views over the lagoon and the Andaman beyond. The interiors pair a modern, light-filled feel with traditional Thai detail drawn from the island.\n\nOpen-plan living and dining flow to a private balcony, with a fully-equipped kitchen for easy in-residence meals. Two bedrooms with quality linens and en-suite bathrooms — one with a bathtub — suit a family or two couples.\n\nThe location is among Phuket’s most connected: roughly 1.4 km to Bang Tao Beach, 2 km to the restaurants and shops of Boat Avenue, and about 3 km to the Laguna golf course, the Cherngtalay temple and the Blue Tree water park. Air-conditioning, ceiling fans, elevator access, a BBQ grill, beach essentials and an in-app concierge complete a comfortable, serviced stay.",
